name: My Window #3
description:
Something that we live every day must be wonderful.
Otherwise, we will lose direction or meaning to catch the moment. 

It's ok, you can say:
But Juan, you are saying how to live to other people.
I would answer:
I only share the tools that help me to survive this system.

It's not easy, but we all together have to share what serves us. To help each other to grow up and live how we want: staying present in our days.
